    "body": "After talking with @gnidan we are going to try initially:\n\n\n- growl notification of tx\n- pending tx view.\n- pending view will have a link to the block explorer (if possible)\n- and then for future the tx view will have the decoded events for the successful tx's from @gnidan feature added in. (stretch)\n\ninitially we will develop this using react.context to store the transactions as I don't think redux may be needed for this feature. ",
